item.title: Indiana Jones game will be released in 2024
item.description: MachineGames Unveils First Look at Indiana Jones and the Great Circle - Xbox Direct 2024 Great news for Indiana Jones fans! A new game based on the franchise is set to be released in 2024. Players will be able to enjoy the game on both PS5 and Steam. Although I haven’t played any games developed by MachineGames yet, I enjoy playing games published by Bethesda. So, I am really excited to try this one!
